A group of Capetonians gathered outside Parliament to protest what they say is a lack of political will. A Cape Town family has started a non-profit company called Mindful Meals to help feeding schemes serve nutritious meals in bulk while cutting costs. A group of Capetonians gathered outside Parliament to protest what they say is a lack of political will. A Cape Town family has started a non-profit company called Mindful Meals to help feeding schemes serve nutritious meals in bulk while cutting costs. A group of Capetonians gathered outside Parliament to protest what they say is a lack of political will. A Cape Town family has started a non-profit company called Mindful Meals to help feeding schemes serve nutritious meals in bulk while cutting costs.